Wheeljack-X::

Jackie turns just in time to see Gatara and Devilcat, the two most 
powerful Rogues, take aim with their weapons.  "Oh, cra-"  The attack 
knocks him flying, and he comes to rest in front of Rodimus, Magnus, 
and (I assume) Nightlight.  "Hiya boss," he groans.
